metadata.name: Evil Empire 3 (Edition of 5)
metadata.description:
The 3rd installment of the Evil Empire series.  

Drawing caparisons between the pop cultures iconic faceless authoritarian menace and modern day police.  A sad reality we are all living through weather experiencing directly or seeing recorded accounts.  Police forces around the world are being associated with aggression and oppression rather than protection and compassion.  
Hiding behind badges and uniforms so they can protect and enable corporate agendas that maintain the status quo that fills the pockets of the rich and wealthy.
